<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" /><title>About Us - Adult Family Home</title><style>* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; } body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; } header { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; padding: 1rem 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; } .header-content { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; } .logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; } nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: opacity 0.3s; } nav a:hover { opacity: 0.8; } .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; } h1 { color: #2D5016; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center; } h2 { color: #2D5016; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #2D5016; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; } .section { margin-bottom: 2rem; } .section p { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; } footer { background-color: #2D5016; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; } .footer-contact { margin-bottom: 1rem; } .footer-contact a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; } .footer-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }</style></head><body><header><div class="header-content"><div class="logo">Adult Family Home</div><nav><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/about">About</a><a href="/services">Services</a><a href="/faq">FAQ</a><a href="/news">News</a><a href="/contact">Contact</a><a href="/legal">Legal</a></nav></div></header><div class="container"><h1>About Us</h1><div class="section"><h2>Our Mission, Values, and Philosophy of Care</h2><p>We believe that aging should be met with dignity, warmth, and respect. Our mission is to provide a safe, comfortable home environment where adults receive personalized care tailored to their unique needs.</p></div><div class="section"><h2>Our Owner and Caregiving Team</h2><p>Matt and Jenny are dedicated caregivers with a deep commitment to senior care. Our caregiving team is trained, compassionate, and present 24/7.</p></div><div class="section"><h2>Our History and Experience in Adult Family Care</h2><p>With extensive background in elder care, Matt and Jenny have built an adult family home that prioritizes both quality of life and person-centered care.</p></div><div class="section"><h2>The Residents We Serve and Our Home-Like Community Size</h2><p>We serve seniors who need assistance with daily living. Our small community size means every resident receives individualized attention.</p></div><div class="section"><h2>Our Commitment to Safety, Licensing, and Quality Care</h2><p>Safety and quality are non-negotiable. We maintain full state licensing and compliance with all adult family home regulations.</p></div></div><footer><div class="footer-contact"><a href="tel:425-123-4567">425-123-4567</a> | <a href="mailto:contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com">contact@afh.wamj@gmail.com</a> | 7am–7pm, 7 days a week</div><p>&copy; 2026 Adult Family Home. All rights reserved.</p><div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><a href="/" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Back to Home</a></div></footer></body></html>
